  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bc7 9 \u0bb5\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf \u0b9a\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b95 \u0ba8\u0baa\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd 3,220 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1 ; 1176 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "3,220 suspects arrested in connection with May 9 violence; 1176 people under arrest",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Investigations related to incidents of violence and rioting during anti-government protests across the country on May 9 are ongoing.",
        "According to the Police Media Unit, 3,220 suspects have been arrested in connection with the said violence so far.",
        "In this case, 3 suspects suspected to be related to the violence that took place in the country on May 9 were arrested during the search operations carried out yesterday and the day before yesterday and two of them have been remanded.",
        "Accordingly, the number of investigations carried out in connection with the violence and riots on May 9 is 858 and the total number of arrests is 3,220. So far, 1,176 of the arrested suspects have been remanded in custody.",
        "The Police Media Unit has informed that the police are conducting further investigations regarding the May 9 violence and riots."
      ],
